<h2 id="numpyamax">numpy.amax</h2>

<p>if you want to get element which has maximun value in desired arrayâ€¦</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="o">&gt;&gt;&gt;</span> <span class="n">a</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">np</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">arange</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="n">reshape</span><span class="p">((</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="mi">2</span><span class="p">))</span>
